item.title: [video] Parkour
item.dc:creator: Winged_One
item.description:
Imonfire:

Sorry to say, but most of this stuff is less than basic. The only thing I thought was good is the cat Jump at 0: 38. The rest is too slow, and the landings are really bad.

NotprobutstillgoodTip: You don’t roll at landing because it looks cool, you roll to absord your landing. At 0:44, you clearly see you (or he) lands on his feet, then jump on the ground to roll. That is totally useless and dangerous if you land from more than seven meters.

Heh, I didn’t see that. I was just skipping around cause I wanted to get to the good parts.

EDIT: Ight, so I watched the video in full. And I will agree with the general census that it was boring and performed dangerously. Still, better then what I can do, so keep at it, I guess. =/

Okay, so he’s not superman. So what? He’s at least marginally good at parkour. Make a video of yourself doing parkour. If you can do as good as he did, then you are allowed to bash him.

So I respect he got that good. Granted, the second video was soooo much better there was almost no comparison.

I’m judging based on the content, not the actual video. If I based it solely on editing/music, the first one sucked balls.

Or do you just resent parkour in general?
